Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:00.75,ef-chs,,0,0,0,,啊 前辈 我是新藤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.05,ef-chs,,0,0,0,,小景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.62,ef-chs,,0,0,0,,能陪我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:17.57,ef-chs,,0,0,0,,这就是… 我吗
